description: Introducing amFilm Premium Screen Protector Film HD Clear (Invisible) for the Samsung Galaxy Tab 2 (10.1-inch) and the Galaxy Note 10.1 (1st Generation/2012 Edition)This amFilm Screen Protector is specifically designed to fit the Galaxy Tab 2 and Note 10.1, and is made from superior quality 3-layer PET film. This HD clear screen protector will not distort the high-definition quality or the natural colors of your display screen. Also, it effectively protects the screen from daily scratches, dust and scrapes. With self-adhering surface, the film is designed for easy application and zero-to-minimal bubbles during application. A squeeze card is also included to remove the occasional bubble easily.Works with:Samsung Galaxy Tab 2Samsung Note 10.1 (1st Generation/2012 Edition)Note: Not compatible with the Note 10.1 2014 Edition TabletContains:2x Screen Protector , Micro-Fiber Cleaning Cloth, Squeeze cardColor:HD Clear (Invisible)Other Samsung screen protector Available on Amazon:Samsung Note 8.0, ASIN: B00CHPGX5WNote: Not compatible with the Note 10.1 2014 Edition TabletTo find the Note 10.1 2014 Edition Screen Protector - Search ASIN B00G02YZ2Q on Amazon.Application:Each of the screen protectors contains 3 layers of PET film. The first and last films are mask films, where the stickers are affixed. The actual screen protector for your device is the film in the middle. Please use the stickers to remove the mask films (NOT the stickers themselves).Warranty:30-Day Money Back GuaranteeLifetime Replacement Warranty
